Girlfriends Get Even 2 - Reality Junkies. Vanessa goes to confront the bitch that is screwing her boyfriend, but instead she meets the hapless guy who is also being deceived. Victoria's loser boyfriend comes home late, drunk, and smelling like cheap perfume, so she makes sure he'll get a rude awakening. Nikki realizes her boyfriend is banging his boss's wife, so she plots with his boss to teach them a lesson. Melanie finds out her boyfriend is using social media to hook up, so she hooks up up on a wild goose chase to free up some time for herself. Lexi's boyfriend is a real dick. When she overhears him convincing his buddy to go out and get laid, she shows his buddy a much easier option.
